sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant LLM as OpenAI-compatible LLM<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as TGIS Generation<br/>8033/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client, Detector: Flow 1: Chat Completions with Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Optional TLS, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>Orch: Chat completion response
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkersService.TokenizeSentence<br/>Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional mTLS, Header passthrough
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: Response (SSE or JSON)<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over Client, Detector: Flow 2: Text Generation with Classification (TGIS)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>TGIS: GenerationService.Generate<br/>gRPC, Optional mTLS
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkersService.TokenizeSentence<br/>Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>Optional mTLS, Header passthrough
    Detector-->>Orch: Classification results
    Orch-->>Client: Classified response (JSON)<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over Client, Detector: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkersService.TokenizeSentence<br/>Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional mTLS, Header passthrough
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: Detection response (JSON)<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over Client, Detector: Flow 4: Streaming Content Detection (NDJSON)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>NDJSON stream, Optional TLS
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkersService (bidirectional streaming)<br/>Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked segments (streaming)
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: NDJSON stream response<br/>Optional TLS
